  ## 🔧 What We Need to Build for Full Grafana Parity

  To replicate these Samsung Health dashboards in Grafana, we need:

  1. BigQuery Views — SQL queries to compute:
      • Daily sleep stage % breakdown
      • Nightly sleep regularity score (computed from std dev of sleep onset time)
      • Sleep efficiency (actual sleep / time in bed)
  2. Grafana Panel Types:
      • Stacked bar chart → sleep stages per night
      • Timeline/Gantt panel → hypnogram (sleep stage timeline)
      • Stat panel → Deep Sleep %, REM %, score
      • Time series → regularity trend over weeks
  3. BigQuery connection — Grafana needs your BigQuery project credentials configured as a data source
